{"tid":1691133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大 家 聽 我 講，唔 好 再 亂 咁 鶳","createTime":"2019-11-03T14:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T06:41:53.000Z","uid":300050,"like":52,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e16c5a9990b29476959e8caa39aff1de5ec55d5c","tid":1691133,"uid":300050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:02:44.000Z","msg":"首先講明先，大家<span style=\"color: red;\">千其</span>唔好鶳人，傷人係犯法架！<br />\n支持警察止暴制亂！<br />\n<br />\n入正題先<br />\n睇live見到有人鶳嘅方法，同打爛仔交無異<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用遮拍頭<br />\n亂打手手腳腳<br />\n扑下塊面咁<br />\n喂，其實大家知唔知啲人鶳係有咩<span style=\"color: blue;\">目的</span>？<br />\n<br />\n啲人唔係純發洩呀<br />\n係對藍絲/狗造成<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">永久傷殘</span></span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果冇永久傷殘，淨係少少擦損/瘀傷/流血，咁唔使鶳啦，佢去急症睇醫生，醫生有工作上嘅責任醫返好佢，而亦係浪費緊公立醫院資源，簡接黎講只係影響咗醫護，冇<span style=\"color: blue;\">實際</span>影響個藍絲狗（藍絲狗反而有機會可獲巨額酬金）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申，我最憎黑衣暴徒架喇，打到人地永久傷殘，係犯法架，<span style=\"color: red;\">千其唔好</span>做。<br />\n<br />\n人體有幾個部位，受傷<span style=\"color: blue;\">致殘</span>機會較高，<span style=\"color: red;\">絕對唔好</span>以身試法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">眼睛</span> （唔使解釋啦）<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">頸動脈</span>（位置：自己摸下自己條頸，前側位置，邊個位脈搏最強，即係摸落個脈搏最「彈手」嗰個位。好學嘅巴絲可以自己google搵解剖圖做學術研究。）<br />\n3. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">頸椎</span>（頸椎神經中樞有頸椎骨包圍保護，要一定力度）<br />\n4. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">手指</span>，特別係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">右手</span>（多數人右手主力手），特別係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">手指公</span>（幻想下你隻手冇咗手指公，隻手仲做到啲乜？）<br />\n5. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">春袋</span>（不解釋）<br />\n6. <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">腳踝關節</span>（影響行動能力）<br />\n<br />\n以上係脆弱位置，傷咗嘅話<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">永久傷殘</span>，醫都難醫，醫返曬藥費，所以絕對不能容許暴徒打人地呢啲位！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且警察接報後好快會黎拉暴徒，所以&mdash;&mdash;<span style=\"color: orange;\">黃金五分鐘</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有暴徒因為冇目標、周身打，打到過曬鐘，畀警察拉！<br />\n如果暴徒只係<span style=\"color: blue;\">針對脆弱位</span>攻擊，可能警察未到已經畀暴徒走甩。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望大家愛好和平，以愛制暴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92e698938217502d73f996bdae362c6261e87ac","tid":1691133,"uid":300013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:04:42.000Z","msg":"直接踩落膝頭哥。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb58915c9a7c9e5be59941e6a161a08cac26de4","tid":1691133,"uid":38904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:08:38.000Z","msg":"胸骨<br />\n除時爆肺都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b825d97031a580bb954c17362dafba3d14b567","tid":1691133,"uid":300050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e92e698938217502d73f996bdae362c6261e87ac","tid":1691133,"uid":300013,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:04:42.000Z","msg":"直接踩落膝頭哥。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:09:08.000Z","msg":"膝關節如果傷到 半月板 或 十字韌帶，或骨折，傷殘較嚴重<br />\n不過唔係個個暴徒都咁大力<br />\n要好大力 + hit啱位先得<br />\n都<span style=\"color: red;\">千其唔好</span>咁做"},{"pid":"ef9583125377be7a23e3c76242a0e1408e1b445b","tid":1691133,"uid":300050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07e622ebc8bfaafa8f41395e567b773b5ca206f8","tid":1691133,"uid":216101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:23:31.000Z","msg":"千奇唔好挖雙眼出黎再踩爆，睇唔到野好慘架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d645130e82d882bedd8adef95f9c389c953abab4","tid":1691133,"uid":75105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:26:16.000Z","msg":"一個手指公插入隻眼再了兩了，可能會導致永久失明。<br />\n<br />\n我高度呼籲各位<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">千其唔好插眼，十分危險！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e909e52352d084d4ec4f15c4060285932ed66c7b","tid":1691133,"uid":300050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"07e622ebc8bfaafa8f41395e567b773b5ca206f8","tid":1691133,"uid":216101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:23:31.000Z","msg":"千奇唔好挖雙眼出黎再踩爆，睇唔到野好慘架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:28:59.000Z","msg":"唔係咁易挖架，有眼球肌連接住<br />\n唔使挖，用利器插到眼球破裂 + 眼球內出血都盲得<br />\n因此必須阻止暴徒咁做！太暴力了！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d0a60c7fd181810ceecca64f6e6ce3d8c30849","tid":1691133,"uid":297152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:31:19.000Z","msg":"真係唔明，點解仲有人用遮嚟拍打人，根本冇力，遮係用嚟篤架嘛。"},{"pid":"4c340ca250e02f386b89dd04f3adedce8064f896","tid":1691133,"uid":300050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38d0a60c7fd181810ceecca64f6e6ce3d8c30849","tid":1691133,"uid":297152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:31:19.000Z","msg":"真係唔明，點解仲有人用遮嚟拍打人，根本冇力，遮係用嚟篤架嘛。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"Nonono<br />\n篤都唔係<br />\n遮係零殺傷力，嚴格黎講係防具唔係武器<br />\n用黎落大雨遮一遮係要嘅<br />\n除非把遮個頭係設計到尖嘅 真係利器咁用"},{"pid":"882e815e516b4a83b732a3d3e36ab8b3c6c5c839","tid":1691133,"uid":178933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:47:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff2e6e5d7297bd80796c9dd634fc4262a99930a","tid":1691133,"uid":130232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:51:25.000Z","msg":"<strong>千祈</strong>唔好整佢條頸呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整傷人哋條頸好大鑊 我哋<strong>唔可以</strong>好似黑警咁呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641b3a3d365825945ad1befb874c9080989e1a67","tid":1691133,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:54:14.000Z","msg":"電光火石不完美"},{"pid":"0a6d421ae78638fff6569570872c262f018735c6","tid":1691133,"uid":189870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:59:45.000Z","msg":"啱呀, 我地要尊重唔同政見人士<br />\n即使係藍絲, 都唔好立亂傷害佢地身體arrrrrr<br />\n大家要冷靜點ar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14258e6685bc970286b778c8da25a3afe15949e","tid":1691133,"uid":189870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a6d421ae78638fff6569570872c262f018735c6","tid":1691133,"uid":189870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T14:59:45.000Z","msg":"啱呀, 我地要尊重唔同政見人士<br />\n即使係藍絲, 都唔好立亂傷害佢地身體arrrrrr<br />\n大家要冷靜點ar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:07:02.000Z","msg":"不完美 可改善"},{"pid":"77a6bad947595deb103185f540701e8bcc1c7001","tid":1691133,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49664e2874de4860494cc34f8e164324ab9dc1a6","tid":1691133,"uid":34793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"斷acl其實係咪冇得斷尾？"},{"pid":"86b841693f874b67fbf5e42cd056cd9e4bcc5cec","tid":1691133,"uid":75965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:18:44.000Z","msg":"咁暴力㗎！！<span style=\"color: red;\">千期唔好咁做</span>"},{"pid":"74c17257dfd41f45904f1b77be97929754e67cb2","tid":1691133,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:20:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eca0b750ec8bdca9db5cf2180630b7bb5ffa872","tid":1691133,"uid":300050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49664e2874de4860494cc34f8e164324ab9dc1a6","tid":1691133,"uid":34793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"斷acl其實係咪冇得斷尾？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"可以做手術repair<br />\n<br />\n但問題係唔係咁易當場整斷<br />\n要有個人識點扭 要有個twisting force<br />\n一來現場好少咁啱有大隻仔  和理非/小朋友居多<br />\n二來藍絲唔會靜止任人扭 會爭扎 仲要同佢鬥埋力"},{"pid":"9b699fc2b41d7d9892d87130da24b83e2034d5f0","tid":1691133,"uid":173072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:27:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">手㬹 - 諗下折木條動作係點, 自己諗下應該點做<br />\n手腕 - 試下自己左手手腕順時針方向轉到盡, 右手手腕逆時針方向轉到盡, 係乜感覺, 如果有人呢個時候大力扭多下會點?<br />\n手肩膀 - 呢個難度高D, 試下伸直隻手, 向背向上, 好似要掂另一隻手ge肩膀, 係咪唔得呢? 諗下伸直隻手, 要向另一隻手向方好似支棒咁推, 可以用埋身體重量加埋支重力點, 咁個重點(肩膀) 會點呢?</span>"},{"pid":"1d421590630e4dba5347d15db04f29a34051a706","tid":1691133,"uid":173072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8eca0b750ec8bdca9db5cf2180630b7bb5ffa872","tid":1691133,"uid":300050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"49664e2874de4860494cc34f8e164324ab9dc1a6","tid":1691133,"uid":34793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"斷acl其實係咪冇得斷尾？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:22:42.000Z","msg":"可以做手術repair<br />\n<br />\n但問題係唔係咁易當場整斷<br />\n要有個人識點扭 要有個twisting force<br />\n一來現場好少咁啱有大隻仔  和理非/小朋友居多<br />\n二來藍絲唔會靜止任人扭 會爭扎 仲要同佢鬥埋力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:28:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">手㬹 - 諗下折木條動作係點, 自己諗下應該點做<br />\n手腕 - 試下自己左手手腕順時針方向轉到盡, 右手手腕逆時針方向轉到盡, 係乜感覺, 如果有人呢個時候大力扭多下會點?<br />\n手肩膀 - 呢個難度高D, 試下伸直隻手, 向背向上, 好似要掂另一隻手ge肩膀, 係咪唔得呢? 諗下伸直隻手, 要向另一隻手向方好似支棒咁推, 可以用埋身體重量加埋支重力點, 咁個重點(肩膀) 會點呢?</span>"},{"pid":"d670b3538089337dab171716ff3b4c6d9a4cccb5","tid":1691133,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:30:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d2e452262502f8806797d2b2215b4e21378d4554","tid":1691133,"uid":300050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T15:52:27.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<br />\n大家幫手推<br />\n救命post黎架"},{"pid":"7b4b13e4c881e8964c98e1dfeee2fe780016766e","tid":1691133,"uid":300050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T00:20:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}